paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the impact of hereditary transthyretin (hATTR) amyloidosis on quality of life, focusing on the NEURO-TTR trial. It mentions the Val30Met TTR mutation but does not provide detailed genetic variant information or penetrance data for TTR variants.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific genetic variant data or penetrance information for TTR variants.
